🔥 Production Scenario

Problem: Nightly backup cron job didn't run.

Investigation

Check cron service:

systemctl status cron

Verify cron jobs:

crontab -l

Check permissions:

ls -l backup.sh

Verify executable:

chmod +x backup.sh

Review cron logs:

Ubuntu:

grep CRON /var/log/syslog

RHEL:

grep CRON /var/log/cron

Test the script manually:

./backup.sh
